OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FLargely cloudy at first, but
OL,6,Fsome brighter spells developing at
OL,7,Ftimes into the afternoon, especially
OL,8,Fin the south. A few spots of rain
OL,9,Fpossible where the cloud thickens,
OL,10,Fmainly over western hills and northern
OL,11,FScotland. Feeling a little warmer.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FShowers largely easing away
OL,14,Fthis evening, but skies remaining
OL,15,Fcloudy. Locally heavy rain across
OL,16,Fnorthwestern areas later in the night.
OL,17,FA mild night under the blanket of
OL,18,Fcloud.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
