OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FCloudy with outbreaks of
OL,6,Frain across northwestern areas, drier
OL,7,Felsewhere with sunny spells developing
OL,8,Fin the south and slowly spreading
OL,9,Fnorth. Feeling warmer, especially in
OL,10,Fthe sunshine in the south.
